<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3937.3.5>
    dc:creator "Komai, Tomoyuki", "Kumar, Appukuttannair Biju", "Reshmi, Rema" ;
    dc:date "2015" ;
    dc:title "A new species of the hermit crab genus Paguristes Dana, 1851 (Crustacea: Decapoda: Anomura: Diogenidae) from southwestern India" ;
    bibo:endPage "532" ;
    bibo:issue "3" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "517" ;
    bibo:volume "3937" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.232473>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.232474>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.232475>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.232476>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.232477>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.232478> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.232473>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Paguristes luculentus n. sp., holotype, male (sl 12.1 mm), ZSI / WGRC / IR / INV. 4148. A, shield and cephalic appendages, dorsal view (right setae omitted); B, carapace, dorsal view (setae omitted); C, left antennule, lateral view; D, anterior part of left branchiostegite and antennal peduncle, lateral view; E, left antennal flagellum, dorsal view; F, telson, dorsal view. Scale bars: 5 mm for A, B, E; 2 mm for C, D, F." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/232473/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.232474>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Paguristes luculentus n. sp., holotype, male (sl 12.1 mm), ZSI / WGRC / IR / INV. 4148 A, left third maxilliped, lateral view; B, dactylus and propodus of left fourth pereopod, lateral view; C, left first gonopod, ventral view; D, same, dorsal view; E, left second gonopod, ventral view. Scale bars: 2 mm for A; 1 mm for B – F." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/232474/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.232475>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Paguristes luculentus n. sp., holotype, male (sl 12.1 mm), ZSI / WGRC / IR / INV. 4148, left cheliped (setae mostly omitted). A, chela and carpus, dorsal view; B, same, mesial view; C, same, lateral view; D, merus, mesial view; E, same, lateral view. Scale bar: 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/232475/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.232476>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Paguristes luculentus n. sp., holotype, male (sl 12.1 mm), ZSI / WGRC / IR / INV. 4148, right cheliped (setae mostly omitted). A, chela, dorsal view; B, entire right cheliped, mesial view; C, same, lateral view; D, carpus, dorsal view. Scale bar: 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/232476/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.232477>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Paguristes luculentus n. sp., holotype, male (sl 12.1 mm), ZSI / WGRC / IR / INV. 4148, ambulatory legs. A, right second pereopod, lateral view; B, left third pereopod, lateral view. Scale bar: 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/232477/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.232478>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Paguristes luculentus n. sp., holotype, male (sl 12.1 mm), ZSI / WGRC / IR / INV. 4148. A – D, right second pereopod, mesial view; E – G, left third pereopod, mesial view (setae mostly omitted). A, E, dactyli; B, F, same, details of tip; C, G, propodi and carpi; D, merus. Scale bars: 2 mm for A, C – E, G; 1 mm for B, F." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/232478/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

